Portuguese_utterance: Mostrar quanto tempo levou desde o primeiro evento de um caso até o evento referente à atividade que indica 'fim da viagem' ou até eventos relacionados a atividades que indicam 'declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário' ou relacionados a atividades que indicam 'pagamento efetuado'.
English_utterance: Show how long it took from the first event of a case to the event related to the activity indicating 'end trip' or to the event related to the activity indicating 'declaration rejected by employee' or the event related to the activity indicating 'payment handled'.
English_SQL_statement: select p.idcase, strftime('%s', p.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'End trip', strftime('%s', x.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Declaration rejected by employee', strftime('%s', y.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Payment handled' from event_log p inner join (select MIN(timestamp) as start_time, idcase FROM event_log GROUP by idcase) e on e.idcase = p.idcase and p.activity = 'End trip' left join event_log x on x.idcase=e.idcase and x.activity = 'Declaration rejected by employee'  left join event_log y on y.idcase=e.idcase and y.activity = 'Payment handled'
Portuguese_SQL_statement: select p.idcase, strftime('%s', p.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Fim da viagem', strftime('%s', x.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário', strftime('%s', y.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Pagamento efetuado' from event_log p inner join (select MIN(timestamp) as start_time, idcase FROM event_log GROUP by idcase) e on e.idcase = p.idcase and p.activity = 'Fim da viagem' left join event_log x on x.idcase=e.idcase and x.activity = 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário'  left join event_log y on y.idcase=e.idcase and y.activity = 'Pagamento efetuado'

Portuguese_utterance: Mostrar quanto tempo levou desde o primeiro evento de um caso até o evento referente ao 'fim da viagem' e até possíveis atividades 'declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário' ou de 'pagamento efetuado'. Ainda, informe o caso e a atividade tratada como final nesse contexto.
English_utterance: Show how long it took from the first event of a case to the event related to 'end trip' and to possible 'declaration rejected by employee' or 'payment handled' activities. Furthermore, report the case and the activity treated as final in this context.
English_SQL_statement: select p.idcase, strftime('%s', p.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'End trip', strftime('%s', x.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Declaration rejected by employee', strftime('%s', y.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Payment handled', f.activity from event_log p inner join (select MIN(timestamp) as start_time, idcase FROM event_log GROUP by idcase) e on e.idcase = p.idcase and p.activity = 'End trip' left join event_log x on x.idcase=e.idcase and x.activity = 'Declaration rejected by employee'  left join event_log y on y.idcase=e.idcase and y.activity = 'Payment handled' inner join (select MAX(timestamp) as end_time, activity, idcase FROM event_log WHERE activity='End trip' or activity= 'Declaration rejected by employee' or activity='Payment handled' GROUP by idcase) f on f.idcase=e.idcase
Portuguese_SQL_statement: select p.idcase, strftime('%s', p.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Fim da viagem', strftime('%s', x.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário', strftime('%s', y.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Pagamento efetuado', f.activity from event_log p inner join (select MIN(timestamp) as start_time, idcase FROM event_log GROUP by idcase) e on e.idcase = p.idcase and p.activity = 'Fim da viagem' left join event_log x on x.idcase=e.idcase and x.activity = 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário' left join event_log y on y.idcase=e.idcase and y.activity = 'Pagamento efetuado' inner join (select MAX(timestamp) as end_time, activity, idcase FROM event_log WHERE activity='Fim da viagem' or activity= 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário' or activity='Pagamento efetuado' GROUP by idcase) f on f.idcase=e.idcase

English_utterance: Show how long it took from the first event of a case to the event related to the 'end trip' or 'declaration rejected by employee' or 'payment handled' activity. In addition to this time, return the case and activity considered at the end of this interval.
English_SQL_statement: select p.idcase, strftime('%s', p.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'End trip', strftime('%s', x.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Declaration rejected by employee', strftime('%s', y.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Payment handled', f.activity from event_log p inner join (select MIN(timestamp) as start_time, idcase FROM event_log GROUP by idcase) e on e.idcase = p.idcase and p.activity = 'End trip' left join event_log x on x.idcase=e.idcase and x.activity = 'Declaration rejected by employee'  left join event_log y on y.idcase=e.idcase and y.activity = 'Payment handled' inner join (select MAX(timestamp) as end_time, activity, idcase FROM event_log WHERE activity='End trip' or activity= 'Declaration rejected by employee' or activity='Payment handled' GROUP by idcase) f on f.idcase=e.idcase
Portuguese_SQL_statement: select p.idcase, strftime('%s', p.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Fim da viagem', strftime('%s', x.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário', strftime('%s', y.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Pagamento efetuado', f.activity from event_log p inner join (select MIN(timestamp) as start_time, idcase FROM event_log GROUP by idcase) e on e.idcase = p.idcase and p.activity = 'Fim da viagem' left join event_log x on x.idcase=e.idcase and x.activity = 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário' left join event_log y on y.idcase=e.idcase and y.activity = 'Pagamento efetuado' inner join (select MAX(timestamp) as end_time, activity, idcase FROM event_log WHERE activity='Fim da viagem' or activity= 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário' or activity='Pagamento efetuado' GROUP by idcase) f on f.idcase=e.idcase

Portuguese_utterance: Qual o tempo de duração médio de cada tipo de atividade?
English_utterance: What is the mean duration time of each type of activity?
English_SQL_statement: WITH RankedEvents AS (SELECT id, activity, timestamp, LEAD(timestamp) OVER (PARTITION BY idcase ORDER BY timestamp) AS next_timestamp, idcase FROM event_log), DurationEvents AS (SELECT activity, (strftime('%s', next_timestamp) - strftime('%s', timestamp)) as duration FROM RankedEvents WHERE next_timestamp IS NOT NULL) SELECT activity, AVG(duration) AS average_duration FROM DurationEvents GROUP BY activity

English_SQL_statement: WITH RankedEvents AS (SELECT id, activity, timestamp, LEAD(timestamp) OVER (PARTITION BY idcase ORDER BY timestamp) AS next_timestamp, idcase FROM event_log), DurationEvents AS (SELECT activity, (strftime('%s', next_timestamp) - strftime('%s', timestamp)) as duration FROM RankedEvents WHERE next_timestamp IS NOT NULL) SELECT activity, AVG(duration) AS average_duration FROM DurationEvents GROUP BY activity

Portuguese_utterance: Qual foi o tempo de duração da atividade 'declaração aprovada pelo supervisor' em cada caso?
English_utterance: What was the duration of the 'declaration approved by supervisor' activity in each case?
English_SQL_statement: WITH RankedEvents AS (SELECT id, activity, timestamp, LEAD(timestamp) OVER (PARTITION BY idcase ORDER BY timestamp) AS next_timestamp, idcase FROM event_log) SELECT idcase, coalesce((strftime('%s', next_timestamp) - strftime('%s', timestamp)),0) as duration FROM RankedEvents WHERE activity='Declaration approved by supervisor'

English_SQL_statement: select strftime('%s', MAX(timestamp)) - strftime('%s', MIN(timestamp)), idcase FROM event_log where idcase in (select idcase from event_log group by idcase having  count(*) IN (select count(*) from event_log group by idcase order by count(*) desc limit 5)) group by idcase
Portuguese_SQL_statement: select strftime('%s', MAX(timestamp)) - strftime('%s', MIN(timestamp)), idcase FROM event_log where idcase in (select idcase from event_log group by idcase having  count(*) IN (select count(*) from event_log group by idcase order by count(*) desc limit 5)) group by idcase

Portuguese_utterance: Quais os dez casos mais recentes em que a atividade 'requisição de pagamento' não foi executada?
English_utterance: What are the ten most recent cases in which the 'request payment' activity was not performed?
English_SQL_statement: SELECT DISTINCT e.idcase FROM event_log AS e join (SELECT idcase, MIN(timestamp) as start_date FROM event_log GROUP BY idcase) AS e1 ON e1.idcase = e.idcase WHERE e.activity = 'Request payment' ORDER BY e1.start_date DESC LIMIT 10
Portuguese_SQL_statement: SELECT DISTINCT e.idcase FROM event_log AS e join (SELECT idcase, MIN(timestamp) as start_date FROM event_log GROUP BY idcase) AS e1 ON e1.idcase = e.idcase WHERE e.activity = 'Requisição de pagamento' ORDER BY e1.start_date DESC LIMIT 10

Portuguese_utterance: Liste todos os casos nos quais dois recursos diferentes executaram a mesma atividade subsequentemente.
English_utterance: List all cases in which two different resources subsequently performed the same activity.

Portuguese_utterance: Quantos eventos ocorreram em cada caso, até que a atividade 'declaração final aprovada pelo diretor' fosse registrada, para os casos em que ela foi registrada?
English_utterance: How many events occurred in each case before the 'declaration final approved by director' activity was recorded, for those cases where it was recorded?
English_SQL_statement: SELECT e.idcase, COUNT(*) FROM event_log e INNER JOIN (SELECT idcase, MIN(timestamp) as timestamp FROM event_log where activity='Declaration final approved by director' GROUP BY idcase order by idcase) e1 on e.idcase = e1.idcase and e.timestamp < e1.timestamp GROUP BY e.idcase
Portuguese_SQL_statement: SELECT e.idcase, COUNT(*) FROM event_log e INNER JOIN (SELECT idcase, MIN(timestamp) as timestamp FROM event_log where activity='Declaração final aprovada pelo diretor' GROUP BY idcase order by idcase) e1 on e.idcase = e1.idcase and e.timestamp < e1.timestamp GROUP BY e.idcase

Portuguese_utterance: Quanto tempo se passou entre a ocorrência da atividade 'permissão requisitada pelo funcionário' e a atividade 'permissão aprovada pela administração', em cada caso nos quais tais atividades ocorreram?
